Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ralph Nader tackles sport
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407jkk
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Oct 1977
US consumer champion Ralph Nader tackles sports organisers to ensure more say for fans. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less